## ğŸ“Œ Sensors Used

### 1ï¸âƒ£ MAX30100 â€“ Heart Rate & SpO2
- I2C device  
- Must be powered using *3.3V only*  
- Use pull-up resistors if readings fluctuate  
- Test code is in MAX30100/test-code/

### 2ï¸âƒ£ GSR Sensor â€“ Anxiety Level
- Analog sensor  
- Connect to ESP32 GPIO34  
- Higher value â†’ higher stress

### 3ï¸âƒ£ MPU6050 / ADXL345 â€“ Fall Detection
- IMU sensor  
- Used for acceleration + orientation  
- Supports AI fall prediction

---

## ğŸ“„ Files Include
- Datasheets  
- Test codes  
- Sensor parameters  
- Calibration instructions

Place all datasheets inside /sensors/SENSOR_NAME/.
