â”‚   â”‚
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ # AI Model â€“ Fall Detection

This folder contains dataset, training scripts, and the final TFLite model for fall detection.

---

## ğŸ§  Model Overview
We use acceleration + gyroscope data from the IMU (MPU6050/ADXL345) to detect:
- Sudden changes in acceleration  
- Orientation shift  
- Activity classification

A neural network is trained on fall vs non-fall samples.

---

## ğŸ“ Folder Details
- training/ â†’ Dataset + notebooks  
- training/train_model.ipynb â†’ Main training notebook  
- training/preprocess.py â†’ Data cleaning  
- exported-model/model.tflite â†’ Final model used in ESP32/Android  
- evaluation/ â†’ Graphs and metrics

---

## ğŸš€ Training Steps
1. Collect IMU data  
2. Preprocess using preprocess.py  
3. Train model in Google Colab  
4. Export to TFLite  
5. Deploy on Android or ESP32 (TinyML)

---

